  "name": "SOC: Compute",
  "description": "Single compute story. Inlines all 7 metric slices sequentially (headline, flow, speed, capacity, patterns, projections, calendar), merges, writes soc_metrics_cache. Triggered by soc_data after a successful sync. Replaces the 7 compute sub-stories and the compute fan-out orchestrator.",
